<h2 id="what-is-your-reward-system">What is your reward system?</h2>

<h2 id="dreamsidealsreality-where-is-the-disconnect">Dreams/Ideals/reality: Where is the disconnect?</h2>
<p>All throughout my time in grad school, I had this dream that I would ride my bike to a park or a beach. I would leave at a civilized time in the morning, around 8 am or so, and read for a few hours, grab a coffee on the way home, and really delight in this process. I did that a few times, certainly less than 10. But every year this dream would resurface ‚Äì especially at the end of Spring quarter. I‚Äôd always say, ‚Äúmaybe this is the year‚Äù. Again, I did that, but not really. I had this dream that I would do that twice a week. Tuesdays and Thursdays. But I never did that. So, what was the hold up?
Papers and books are heavy.
Parks are dirty and windy.
But maybe I didn‚Äôt want that?</p>

